1
00:01:40,820 --> 00:01:45,940
[THE DEVIL BETWEEN US]

2
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:49,020
[Episode 1]

3
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,140
I've paid.

4
00:01:56,170 --> 00:01:56,940
Okay.

5
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:59,050
Two buns, please.

6
00:01:59,410 --> 00:02:00,340
Coming right up.

7
00:02:01,970 --> 00:02:07,440
[7:58AM, Saturday, Nuanhai Town,
Nuanfeng County, Haizhou City]

8
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:15,260
[Qin, Narcotics Brigade,
Nuanfeng County PSB, Haizhou City]

9
00:02:15,350 --> 00:02:19,579
[Tan Jie, Narcotics Brigade,
Nuanfeng County PSB, Haizhou City]

10
00:02:19,070 --> 00:02:19,900
What time is it?

11
00:02:19,730 --> 00:02:22,110
[Guo Bo & Mu Ying, Narcotics Brigade,
Nuanfeng County PSB, Haizhou City]

12
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,320
Around 8 a.m.

13
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:25,350
[Jin Longfeng, Narcotics Unit,
Haizhou City Public Security Bureau]

14
00:02:24,150 --> 00:02:24,880
Captain Jin,

15
00:02:24,900 --> 00:02:27,120
is your intel
from the city bureau reliable?

16
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,600
[Wenyuan Hotel]

17
00:02:27,190 --> 00:02:29,770
We've been staking out
for days here in the county.

18
00:02:29,770 --> 00:02:32,050
Could Ding Lai just be messing with us?

19
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:35,280
The tip says there's a high probability

20
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,680
he's dealing in Nuanfeng County this time.

21
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:39,960
You guys know the county better.

22
00:02:39,980 --> 00:02:41,180
Just hang in there.

23
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,360
Here he comes.

24
00:03:23,410 --> 00:03:24,840
Car 2, get ready to move.

25
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:26,520
Copy that.

26
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:36,990
Car 2 is moving.

27
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:38,490
We're right behind you.

28
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:39,840
Copy that.

29
00:03:52,050 --> 00:03:52,680
Team 2,

30
00:03:53,079 --> 00:03:55,060
the target is heading
toward the urban area.

31
00:03:55,060 --> 00:03:57,040
We're sharing his position in real-time.

32
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:58,840
Be ready to assist at any moment.

33
00:03:59,650 --> 00:04:00,500
Copy that.

34
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,590
I wonder if these two

35
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:12,840
are up to something new today.

36
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:19,750
Target vehicle made a U-turn
at the city exit.

37
00:04:19,750 --> 00:04:21,190
Suspicious behavior.

38
00:04:22,390 --> 00:04:23,150
Stay close.

39
00:04:25,310 --> 00:04:27,420
Car 1 has tailed too long.
Switch to Car 2.

40
00:04:27,420 --> 00:04:28,210
Copy that.

41
00:04:38,070 --> 00:04:40,640
[Hu Wenjing, Recognized as Outstanding
Police Officer of Nuanfeng County]

42
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:53,120
We want to eat.

43
00:04:49,930 --> 00:04:52,440
[Hu Wenjing, Detective,
Nuanfeng County PSB, Haizhou City]

44
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:53,870
Stop fussing.

45
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:54,430
Eat your food.

46
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:55,810
Didn't I say to eat properly?

47
00:04:55,810 --> 00:04:56,270
If you keep this up,

48
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:57,480
you're skipping flute class today.

49
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,930
I'll send you straight to Aunt Xiaoya's.

50
00:04:58,930 --> 00:04:59,990
You want to go, huh?

51
00:05:00,390 --> 00:05:01,870
Be good. Sit and eat.

52
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,350
Look at your mom.

53
00:05:04,370 --> 00:05:05,600
It's fine on weekdays,

54
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:08,020
but even on her day off,
she's as busy as if she was in battle.

55
00:05:08,020 --> 00:05:09,520
That's because you're slacking.

56
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:10,910
Me? Slacking?

57
00:05:11,310 --> 00:05:12,120
Hu Wenjing,

58
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:13,950
didn't I help you raise the two kids?

59
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:15,680
Do you know how hard it is
to lead a team now?

60
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,430
You call this helping?

61
00:05:16,430 --> 00:05:17,750
You three are in cahoots.

62
00:05:17,750 --> 00:05:18,270
Zhi.

63
00:05:18,570 --> 00:05:19,280
Yes.

64
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:19,740
Ming.

65
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:20,320
Yes.

66
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:21,310
You hear that?

67
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,670
We three are in cahoots.

68
00:05:25,750 --> 00:05:26,680
What was our agreement?

69
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,040
Repeat it, both of you. Now.

70
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:28,560
No fighting.

71
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,160
No skipping class.

72
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,120
No getting the teacher
to call our parents.

73
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,190
I have no expectations

74
00:05:31,190 --> 00:05:31,870
about how well

75
00:05:31,870 --> 00:05:33,240
you play the flute.

76
00:05:33,260 --> 00:05:35,000
Just don't get expelled.

77
00:05:35,020 --> 00:05:36,190
If you get kicked out,

78
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:37,560
it'll be Math Olympiad class for you.

79
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,360
Understood?

80
00:05:38,750 --> 00:05:40,680
Don't let the bag strap
wrinkle your clothes

81
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,680
Wang Ping!

82
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:42,720
Wenjing!

83
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,680
Move it, you little rascals.

84
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,040
Hurry up.

85
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,070
You're gonna be late.

86
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:45,510
Wait.

87
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:46,360
Say hi to Wenjing.

88
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,360
Auntie Wang Ping!

89
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:48,950
You two here for school?

90
00:05:48,950 --> 00:05:50,120
You're late. Hurry up.

91
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,040
Go on.

92
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:51,600
Bye.

93
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,159
Watch your step.

94
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:53,270
Pay attention in class.

95
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:53,800
Bye.

96
00:05:53,820 --> 00:05:54,460
Say hello.

97
00:05:54,610 --> 00:05:55,300
Hello, Wenjing.

98
00:05:55,300 --> 00:05:55,909
Wang An.

99
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,010
I'm going in.

100
00:05:57,390 --> 00:05:58,120
Hey,

101
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,120
what do you want for dinner?

102
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,600
Text me in advance,

103
00:06:00,650 --> 00:06:01,780
and I'll prepare it.

104
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:04,040
Why is the strap off your shoulder again?

105
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,120
How many times have I told you?

106
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,070
You'll get uneven shoulders.

107
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:08,160
You worry way more than I do.

108
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:10,710
You're more like a mom than a sister.

109
00:06:10,850 --> 00:06:11,790
What's the deal with him?

110
00:06:11,790 --> 00:06:14,150
This is his third year
taking the exam, right?

111
00:06:14,150 --> 00:06:16,270
If he doesn't pass this year,

112
00:06:16,300 --> 00:06:17,300
what's your plan?

113
00:06:17,630 --> 00:06:18,480
Xiaoya's already here.

114
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,120
Let's hurry.

115
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:21,050
Why are you avoiding the question?

116
00:06:34,790 --> 00:06:36,080
Xiaoya, you're here.

117
00:06:36,450 --> 00:06:36,890
Let me.

118
00:06:37,650 --> 00:06:39,909
Is everything prepared as I instructed?

119
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:40,630
Xiaoya,

120
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:42,360
I've been swamped today.

121
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,190
I didn't have time to check my phone,

122
00:06:44,190 --> 00:06:45,510
so I missed your message.

123
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:47,360
Is it still three people today?

124
00:06:47,380 --> 00:06:48,580
Yes, still three.

125
00:06:50,500 --> 00:06:51,900
Sorry about that.

126
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,510
Your usual table

127
00:06:53,510 --> 00:06:54,610
is taken today.

128
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:56,590
But you can sit nearby for now.

129
00:06:56,630 --> 00:06:57,750
Once it clears up,

130
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:58,830
I'll move you over.

131
00:06:59,040 --> 00:06:59,560
That's fine.

132
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,510
I'll just sit there for now.

133
00:07:00,510 --> 00:07:00,920
Okay.

134
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,870
This way.

135
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,570
Here are your things.

136
00:07:06,570 --> 00:07:07,210
Give them to me.

137
00:07:07,210 --> 00:07:07,540
Okay.

138
00:07:18,180 --> 00:07:19,780
This place they picked today

139
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,160
feels a bit off.

140
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,890
Looks like something's up.

141
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:25,450
All units, attention.

142
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,510
Ding Lai is very likely

143
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:28,110
making the deal in this cafe.

144
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:29,480
Hello, how many in your party?

145
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,750
Two. We'll sit upstairs.

146
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:31,240
Okay.

147
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:31,970
Tan Jie,

148
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,159
you two go up and keep watch.

149
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:33,800
Be careful.

150
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,510
Keep your distance from Ding Lai.

151
00:07:35,510 --> 00:07:36,240
What can I get you?

152
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,440
I'll look at the menu.

153
00:07:52,860 --> 00:07:54,740
Wu, go check the back door area.

154
00:07:53,860 --> 00:07:55,730
[Wu Jun, Narcotics Brigade,
Haizhou City Public Security Bureau]

155
00:07:55,580 --> 00:07:56,180
Copy that.

156
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:00,800
Captain Jin,

157
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,620
the back door leads to a market.

158
00:08:02,620 --> 00:08:03,210
It's crowded,

159
00:08:03,210 --> 00:08:04,140
chaotic,

160
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,280
and hard to secure.

161
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,810
We're short-handed.

162
00:08:12,190 --> 00:08:15,190
Request backup
from the county brigade immediately.

163
00:08:15,670 --> 00:08:17,710
They chose this spot to meet the seller

164
00:08:17,710 --> 00:08:19,440
probably because of the crowd.

165
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,070
Even if the police raid,

166
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:22,970
they wouldn't dare open fire.

167
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,560
Wang Ping.

168
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,530
Wenjing.

169
00:08:25,980 --> 00:08:26,580
Over here.

170
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:27,720
Xiaoya.

171
00:08:28,210 --> 00:08:28,740
Why...

172
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:29,830
Why are you sitting here?

173
00:08:29,830 --> 00:08:31,230
Yeah, not our usual spot.

174
00:08:31,540 --> 00:08:32,110
The people there haven't left yet.

175
00:08:32,110 --> 00:08:33,909
We can move there later.

176
00:08:33,909 --> 00:08:34,840
Let's sit here for now.

177
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,440
Okay.

178
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,549
You're quite on time today.

179
00:08:37,549 --> 00:08:38,510
Of course.

180
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:40,030
You dressed like a ghost again.

181
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:41,429
I came just to scare you.

182
00:08:41,450 --> 00:08:42,120
How do I look?

183
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:42,630
Beautiful.

184
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:43,230
Very beautiful.

185
00:08:43,230 --> 00:08:43,720
Am I beautiful?

186
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,080
Yeah.

187
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,570
How are things with Cheng Xiaodong?

188
00:08:45,570 --> 00:08:46,900
You just ask directly?

189
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:48,140
Seriously.

190
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,380
I don't even want to talk about him.

191
00:08:49,380 --> 00:08:49,960
Let me tell you,

192
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,390
Cheng Xiaodong is hopeless now.

193
00:08:51,390 --> 00:08:51,840
What happened?

194
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,310
He's obsessed with fishing.

195
00:08:53,310 --> 00:08:54,700
And you know what?

196
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:57,120
Ordinary fishing spots
don't satisfy him anymore.

197
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,640
He has to rent a fishing boat.

198
00:08:58,640 --> 00:08:59,390
I'm definitely

199
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:00,450
getting a divorce.

200
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,620
Ding Lai is on the move.

201
00:09:04,290 --> 00:09:05,420
Tan Jie, follow him.

202
00:09:18,890 --> 00:09:19,560
Wu,

203
00:09:19,930 --> 00:09:21,530
Ding Lai is heading your way.

204
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,410
What are you doing here?

205
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,920
Looking for someone.

206
00:09:57,150 --> 00:09:58,150
Which room?

207
00:09:59,230 --> 00:10:00,040
8401.

208
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,530
It's upstairs.

209
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:33,500
Who's it?

210
00:10:35,670 --> 00:10:37,070
I'm Wishes Come True.

211
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:46,630
Hello.

212
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:47,720
You're...

213
00:10:48,390 --> 00:10:49,840
Great Luck 2016?

214
00:10:49,970 --> 00:10:51,720
We talked on the forum.

215
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:53,460
Take off your mask.

216
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,240
Mask!

217
00:11:12,930 --> 00:11:13,990
Where's the money?

218
00:11:15,140 --> 00:11:15,850
I...

219
00:11:26,860 --> 00:11:28,260
Where's the thing I want?

220
00:11:29,100 --> 00:11:30,190
Money first,

221
00:11:30,670 --> 00:11:31,530
then the goods.

222
00:11:32,150 --> 00:11:34,610
I already transferred
30,000 to you online.

223
00:11:35,510 --> 00:11:36,440
For the remaining 70,000,

224
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,550
we agreed on

225
00:11:37,610 --> 00:11:39,440
cash on delivery.

226
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:19,660
Money first,

227
00:12:19,870 --> 00:12:20,910
then the goods.

228
00:12:36,590 --> 00:12:37,640
70,000.

229
00:12:44,890 --> 00:12:46,680
Can I see the goods then?

230
00:12:54,490 --> 00:12:55,690
He just went to the restroom.

231
00:12:55,690 --> 00:12:56,950
Everything is normal.

232
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:00,960
How are things with you?

233
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:02,000
Transferred to the City Bureau?

234
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:02,790
Just finished the exam.

235
00:13:02,790 --> 00:13:03,860
I'm waiting for results.

236
00:13:03,860 --> 00:13:05,450
Dai doesn't really want to let me go.

237
00:13:05,450 --> 00:13:06,480
I said it's for the kids,

238
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,650
so he can't really argue, right?

239
00:13:07,650 --> 00:13:08,560
But I think

240
00:13:08,590 --> 00:13:10,670
you're just causing yourself
unnecessary trouble.

241
00:13:10,670 --> 00:13:12,550
With those two little terrors of yours

242
00:13:12,550 --> 00:13:13,240
being so wild,

243
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,000
always acting up,

244
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,120
do you think a school in the city

245
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,480
can handle them?

246
00:13:16,630 --> 00:13:17,440
They can't.

247
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:17,840
Then where?

248
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,510
You should just

249
00:13:18,510 --> 00:13:20,630
move straight to the provincial capital.

250
00:13:20,630 --> 00:13:22,150
Send them to an international school.

251
00:13:22,150 --> 00:13:23,790
I really regret it now.

252
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:25,390
I should have left back then.

253
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:27,320
If I had gone abroad,

254
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,240
wouldn't I be better off than now?

255
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,030
Here we go again.

256
00:13:29,030 --> 00:13:29,870
Just think about it.

257
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:31,360
Even if I were washing dishes abroad,

258
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:33,070
I'd feel my life had purpose.

259
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,910
Washing dishes, really?

260
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:36,600
Let her try a couple of days
at our electronics factory.

261
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,970
She definitely wouldn't
be able to handle it.

262
00:13:37,970 --> 00:13:39,250
That's true.

263
00:13:39,510 --> 00:13:40,750
But regarding your online business,

264
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:41,790
it doesn't matter

265
00:13:41,790 --> 00:13:42,870
whether you're here or abroad.

266
00:13:42,870 --> 00:13:45,120
Don't you just operate it
on your phone anyway?

267
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:47,120
Besides, you make so much money
from this business, right?

268
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:47,950
This meal is on you.

269
00:13:47,950 --> 00:13:48,670
The next one is on you too.

270
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:49,480
The next one is still on her.

271
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:50,910
It's on you forever.

272
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:51,840
No problem.

273
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:52,840
It's all on me.

274
00:13:52,860 --> 00:13:53,410
Great.

275
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:02,790
Why isn't anyone here yet?

276
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:05,050
What's the rush?

277
00:14:18,950 --> 00:14:20,010
What are you doing?

278
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,620
Still can't get it out?

279
00:14:21,740 --> 00:14:22,600
What's taking you so long?

280
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,660
What are you doing?

281
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:30,190
Where's the thing I want?

282
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,000
Right here.

283
00:14:31,670 --> 00:14:33,200
Just smuggled from abroad.

284
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,050
Untraceable.

285
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:35,010
Very safe.

286
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:38,920
I just want a kidney.

