587
00:32:03,270 --> 00:32:03,870
Xiaodong.

588
00:32:05,820 --> 00:32:06,940
There's one thing.

589
00:32:07,440 --> 00:32:08,200
I've thought about it,

590
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:10,050
and you're the only one I can talk to.

591
00:32:10,050 --> 00:32:12,250
Jiajia needs more money for treatment?

592
00:32:12,790 --> 00:32:14,980
I can spare over 20,000.

593
00:32:15,110 --> 00:32:15,940
If you need it,

594
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:17,000
I'll transfer it to you.

595
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:18,090
No.

596
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:19,420
It's not about Jiajia.

597
00:32:20,590 --> 00:32:21,350
But...

598
00:32:21,940 --> 00:32:23,400
what I'm about to tell you,

599
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:25,290
you must keep it secret.

600
00:32:25,960 --> 00:32:26,900
Okay, go ahead.

601
00:32:34,400 --> 00:32:35,390
Tell me.

602
00:32:36,750 --> 00:32:37,670
Go ahead.

603
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:39,270
I have things to do.

604
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:42,460
Xiaoya asked me
to pick up her friend's kids.

605
00:32:44,840 --> 00:32:45,710
You go ahead.

606
00:32:45,990 --> 00:32:46,660
We'll talk later.

607
00:32:46,660 --> 00:32:47,790
It's not urgent.

608
00:32:49,130 --> 00:32:49,610
Okay.

609
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:50,580
Hanging up.

610
00:33:05,310 --> 00:33:06,310
Are you full?

611
00:33:49,440 --> 00:33:50,270
My turn.

612
00:33:50,780 --> 00:33:51,660
Let me have another round.

613
00:33:51,660 --> 00:33:52,420
We're here.

614
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,890
We said one round each.

615
00:33:56,940 --> 00:33:57,530
Get off.

616
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:00,710
Careful.

617
00:34:01,920 --> 00:34:03,480
Wait for me. Let me see.

618
00:34:04,460 --> 00:34:05,240
Play when we get home.

619
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:05,760
Hurry.

620
00:34:07,320 --> 00:34:08,270
Take off your shoes.

621
00:34:08,270 --> 00:34:09,130
See?

622
00:34:09,710 --> 00:34:11,150
It's not fit.

623
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:12,800
Sweethearts,

624
00:34:13,159 --> 00:34:15,290
it's been so long since you visited me.

625
00:34:16,510 --> 00:34:18,150
I'll go make you something good to eat.

626
00:34:18,150 --> 00:34:19,120
Don't bother, Mom.

627
00:34:19,120 --> 00:34:20,230
We just ate on the way here.

628
00:34:20,230 --> 00:34:21,300
That won't do.

629
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:22,949
The kids rarely get to visit.

630
00:34:24,429 --> 00:34:26,690
Hu Wenjing might pick them up a bit later.

631
00:34:29,030 --> 00:34:29,880
Just wait.

632
00:34:30,190 --> 00:34:32,650
let me give you some
taro and lotus seed soup.

633
00:34:32,679 --> 00:34:33,469
Okay.

634
00:34:33,489 --> 00:34:35,889
-Thank you, Grandma.
-Thank you, Grandma.

635
00:34:37,170 --> 00:34:38,370
Look at the time.

636
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:40,719
Is Li Xiaoya coming back to stay or not?

637
00:34:40,850 --> 00:34:41,730
Probably busy.

638
00:34:43,199 --> 00:34:45,989
When are you two
signing the divorce papers?

639
00:34:47,620 --> 00:34:48,370
We'll see.

640
00:34:50,710 --> 00:34:52,590
This can't be delayed.

641
00:34:54,889 --> 00:34:55,889
Let me tell you,

642
00:34:56,270 --> 00:34:58,340
the debt collectors came again today.

643
00:34:58,340 --> 00:35:01,390
I was so scared I hid in my room
and didn't dare make a sound.

644
00:35:01,390 --> 00:35:03,180
They were shouting outside,

645
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:04,640
said they'd paint the walls

646
00:35:04,640 --> 00:35:06,500
and write slogans if we don't pay.

647
00:35:06,610 --> 00:35:08,260
All the neighbors heard it.

648
00:35:08,540 --> 00:35:10,870
How am I supposed
to show my face in public?

649
00:35:11,020 --> 00:35:12,280
Mom, the kids are here.

650
00:35:14,640 --> 00:35:15,900
I don't want a divorce.

651
00:35:16,000 --> 00:35:17,080
I'll pay her debts.

652
00:35:18,780 --> 00:35:20,320
Why should you?

653
00:35:22,990 --> 00:35:25,020
You've always been giving her money.

654
00:35:25,020 --> 00:35:26,760
She got herself into these debts.

655
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:27,920
What does it have to do with you?

656
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:28,590
Besides...

657
00:35:28,590 --> 00:35:29,710
Enough.

658
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:30,590
I've had a long day.

659
00:35:30,590 --> 00:35:31,190
Let me take a nap.

660
00:35:31,190 --> 00:35:32,650
She shouldn't burden you.

661
00:35:32,920 --> 00:35:34,320
Can't you see?

662
00:35:35,950 --> 00:35:37,010
You're so useless.

663
00:36:01,250 --> 00:36:02,370
Don't litter.

664
00:36:11,230 --> 00:36:13,430
Even the basic blood type didn't match.

665
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:19,480
He sent me the matching report.

666
00:36:20,980 --> 00:36:21,980
I got scammed.

667
00:36:22,150 --> 00:36:22,820
How much?

668
00:36:25,140 --> 00:36:26,190
100,000.

669
00:36:29,990 --> 00:36:31,200
I told you long ago.

670
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:32,510
The online black market isn't reliable.

671
00:36:32,510 --> 00:36:33,670
But you wouldn't listen.

672
00:36:33,670 --> 00:36:35,280
If you just wait in line,
you could get a kidney.

673
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:36,990
You say that every time!

674
00:36:37,210 --> 00:36:38,110
Wait until when?

675
00:36:38,110 --> 00:36:38,850
This year?

676
00:36:47,010 --> 00:36:47,940
Don't rush.

677
00:36:48,290 --> 00:36:49,200
Be patient.

678
00:36:55,610 --> 00:36:57,090
I just hate seeing Jiajia

679
00:36:57,630 --> 00:36:59,690
suffer through dialysis every time.

680
00:37:00,950 --> 00:37:01,790
Me too.

681
00:37:02,600 --> 00:37:04,460
But does acting recklessly help?

682
00:37:04,710 --> 00:37:05,630
Growing up,

683
00:37:05,650 --> 00:37:08,250
when has taking a shortcut
ever worked for you?

684
00:37:08,400 --> 00:37:10,660
You should just wait for the relief fund.

685
00:37:14,990 --> 00:37:16,250
Stop eating. Let's go.

686
00:37:19,850 --> 00:37:21,770
Let's go.

687
00:37:25,100 --> 00:37:26,960
I'll figure out the money myself.

688
00:37:32,350 --> 00:37:34,240
Xiaoyu, look at this mosquito.

689
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:35,940
-Tao?
-It's kissing someone.

690
00:37:37,370 --> 00:37:37,800
How are things?

691
00:37:37,800 --> 00:37:39,060
Pretty good recently.

692
00:37:39,660 --> 00:37:40,520
I'm doing okay.

693
00:37:43,980 --> 00:37:45,270
Actually, I have...

694
00:37:46,010 --> 00:37:47,900
a favor to ask.

695
00:37:48,890 --> 00:37:50,120
I have a niece.

696
00:37:51,600 --> 00:37:53,840
She has some intellectual disabilities.

697
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:54,510
And there's been

698
00:37:54,510 --> 00:37:56,840
some trouble at home lately.

699
00:37:57,590 --> 00:37:58,590
I was wondering

700
00:37:58,590 --> 00:38:01,070
if I could send her to your place

701
00:38:01,070 --> 00:38:02,360
to stay for a while.

702
00:38:03,070 --> 00:38:04,000
If that's okay,

703
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:06,480
I'll bring her over tomorrow morning.

704
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:07,480
What do you think?

705
00:38:09,630 --> 00:38:10,230
Okay.

706
00:38:10,630 --> 00:38:11,400
Thanks.

707
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:12,400
Thanks.

708
00:38:12,510 --> 00:38:13,510
Thanks, brother.

709
00:38:14,560 --> 00:38:15,090
Okay.

710
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:16,440
See you tomorrow.

711
00:38:42,270 --> 00:38:49,080
[Next Episode Preview]
